---script_Invulnerability_IncomingDamage---
additionalDamage = -1 * damage

---script_raidportal1_Monster---
// This script ensures the portal remains stationary and doesn't attack
if !isDead {
	addAuraToEntity(myEntityId, "Invulnerability", 0, myEntityId)
}